'''''Polyhedron'' 68''' was a roleplaying magazine from [[February]] of [[1992]]. It contained many roleplaying articles, including a rules supplement for the [[West End Games]] ''[[Star Wars]]'' [[Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game|D6]] system. The article was called "[[Iron Hands, Captive Hearts]]" and was written by [[Joe Littrell]]. Like all supplements printed in ''[[Polyhedron]]'' prior to [[2002]], the article is considered ambiguously [[canon]].

